  "passage": [
    "The sky is pink at dawn. Dew shines on the grass. Sam and Lina go into the garden with Dad. |“Look—tiny footprints!” says Lina.",
    "They kneel by the mud. A small trail runs past the flower bed. Some prints are V-shaped. Others are round with four little dots. |“Two kinds,” says Dad.",
    "They follow the trail to the gate. The V-prints go towards the bird feeder. The round paw prints stop at the gate latch. A soft tuft of fur is stuck there.",
    "Sam and Lina compare the shapes and sizes. |“A bird hopped to the feeder, and a cat came to the gate,” says Dad. They draw the prints in a notebook. |“Mystery solved!”"
  ],
